            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Mummio <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Hispano <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> cives et incolae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex cert="low">unicipes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> Flavii <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>eri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sing</abbr><ex>iliensis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>ex aere conlato <lb n="6"/>ob merita dederunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zylinderförmige Statuenbasis. Im 16. Jh. wurde eine Kopie der Inschrift auf einer Tafel angefertigt und diese im Arco de los Gigantes vermauert.</p>
            </div>
